messages.title: Competent leadership
messages.content: Job total hits record high while wages surge.

messages.title: Coalition of chaos
messages.content: Labour plan to borrow risks £170bn extra debt.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: OUR COMMITMENTS TO CONTROL IMMIGRATION AND DELIVER THE TOUGHEST WELFARE SYSTEM for EU migrants anywhere in the EU.

issues.brexitEurope: EU migrants should have a job offer before they come; not to come and live off benefits; give you say on Europe in an in/out referendum by the end of 2017.
issues.economy: Job total hits record high while wages surge; Labour plan to borrow risks £170bn extra debt; More debt, Higher taxes, Jobs lost.
issues.immigration: OUR COMMITMENTS TO CONTROL IMMIGRATION for EU migrants; no free access to our welfare system; not to claim tax credits, child benefit or social housing from Britain unless they have been here for at least four years.
issues.socialWelfare: Deliver the toughest welfare system for EU migrants anywhere in the EU; no free access to our welfare system for at least four years.

images.caption: Leaflet page showing conservative commitments to control immigration and the claim that Labour and SNP create chaos.
